{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_146","type":"agent_message","text":"There’s an existing pattern in the repo for Akka/Pekko protobuf: they register `sun.misc.Unsafe` itself plus the private `theUnsafe` field. I’m comparing that with Akka actor’s `akka.util.Unsafe` initialization now, since the new failure is an `Unsafe` bootstrap problem rather than another missing app class."}}
